  }}
</p>
<hr class="light">
<h2 class="au-display-lg" id="workers-compensation">
  <b>Workers’ compensation insurance</b>
</h2>
<p>
  Your workers’ compensations insurance must cover the same number of employees as you selected in the company details section of this application. We understand there may be discrepancies, for example due to the part-time or casual nature of your employees, if so please provide details.
</p>
